    *Bug found in previous version: If the Delete Edging button on the edge softening page was pressed after the frames of a video were edged then on some occasions the program would erroneously not show a message saying that the edging can only be deleted on the Custom page. Is such a case as this, if the program erroneously allows a deletion then the result is that the program 'thinks' that no edging was done when in fact it was done. This bug has been fixed.\par
