    A new version of VirtualU has been uploaded because of the change shown below.\par
    *The Help files have been updated.\par
    *User prompts, instructions and information windows have been updated.\par
    *Very rare bug found: On one occasion while a build was occurring on the Film Options page a user prompt appeared and erroneously listed the filename of a video which would be converted because its frame rate was not evenly divisible into the project frame rate. In fact its frame did actually divide evenly into the project frame rate. We were unable to duplicate the error but we added some new code to the program which should fix this bug.\par
