                                                                  April 25, 2022\par
    No new version of VirtualU is available or needed at this time. This is an update of coming attractions.\par
    We are very pleased to report that the next version of the edge softening page will have a new tool titled "Tools\\Use Special Internal Edge Softening (System 3)". The SoftType internal edging systems perform edge softening on interior foreground solid colors which are partially or completely surrounded by a color other than the background color of the image. It has been our continuous goal to develop an internal edging system that provides the same quality as the SoftType external edging system and the new tool accomplishes that.\par
    Internal Systems 1 and 2 can edge some colors as well as the new System 3 and they provide other options so they will be retained, providing good coverage of all situations.\par
    The new edging page will also provide speed information about the three internal edging systems. There are actually four internal systems since the Hybrid system offers standard and alternate options of operations.\par
    The new edging page will be available for download within a few days. Once again, the main program will be the same so only the edging page (edges1.exe) will need to be downloaded by anyone who already has VirtualU.\par
\par
