    *New tool: The main edge softening page has a new video player called Play Video which always starts the playback at the first frame and then plays all the extracted video frames.\par
    *Bad bug found: To our horror we discovered that an attempt to start the main edge softening page to alter a picture would result in a crash. Videos were not affected. This was a serious problem but not a catastrophe since the main program was unaffected except that the program would at some point automatically prompt the user to reset the edging page, though pictures could not be loaded onto the edge softening page. This bug has been fixed.\par
    *New tool: The main edge softening has a new tool that enables the user to fine tune the playback speed when the project is played using Play Project.\par
