    A new version of VirtualU is available for download and it's a big one.\par
    *Improvement made: We have found on some occasions that some chosen areas (usually backgrounds) of imported picture and video images would not go transparent when desired because their widths and/or heights did not end in zero. The program now checks the size dimensions of an image when it is imported. If the image is a non-standard size then the user is alerted to this potential problem and given solutions.\par
