    *New tool: The Custom page has a new zoom tool titled "Special\\Zoom up from or down to a pinpoint" and this tool is known as Zoom 2. It zooms transparent and non-transparent pictures and the frames of videos. It has a wide speed range and it makes high quality AVI videos that you import and use in a project. No matter what speed is used, the action in every zoom is smooth. It has built-in smoothness. Zoom 2 does almost everything automatically for the user.\par
    *The tool Clean Interior in the Rotation page toolkit has been updated to specifically soften the interiors of Zoom 2 videos made from pictures and videos. This tool softens only the frames of a Zoom 2 video that need softening and leaves other frames alone. \par
