    The biggest fix involved the "Misc.\\Record Fast Forward" tool on the Playback/Recording page which was prone to problems and even freezes. This tool has been completely overhauled and repaired. In fact, this work paved the way for several new tools including a video splicer and an incremental speed player with which a user may move quickly back and forth through a video.\par
